{"tid":2117931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"笑撚死 入去呢個post睇一睇 原來連登屌醫護惡過屌狗","createTime":"2020-07-21T07:12:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T09:25:13.000Z","uid":49524,"like":24,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a1cbbc3d3bfa657ce931f31481180844a8407c55","tid":2117931,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:12:50.000Z","msg":"醫護低賤過地底泥 本年度凍薪<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2117862\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2117862</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n先唔評論醫護係咪自己友<br />\n原來做野盡責過狗都仲要俾人口殊筆伐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喂你老母 今日咩日子呀？！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n72ADrj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn72ADrj.jpg&h=8f091b48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來大家原諒左狗隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個武漢肺炎令醫護比狗更可恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個失敗嘅罷工就令醫護唔係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ca3aabcf8cb3795489158fd884b40c751dec95","tid":2117931,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f83ead41fc0d9d3d2e243c57e378bf1a3e986e6","tid":2117931,"uid":49524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:15:04.000Z","msg":"精選721post<br />\n<br />\n721元朗警署內30警拒絕出動片段流出：喂全部同事入返去先<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2117184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2117184</a><br />\n<br />\n「特發」721元朗雞地無碼 CCTV流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2117269\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2117269</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7546d1d02e67d26be8db88a2990dd2995b1f6143","tid":2117931,"uid":258258,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:15:58.000Z","msg":"之前仲有人叫醫護再罷，有登仔呢D咁激烈既支持，實會再罷啦<img src=\"/assets/f