img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85ea2cdd761b232bd7c64c2d0192aa1d9547f13","tid":2117931,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"626130020a8e6200aed90812ccc540eb16ba7e69","tid":2117931,"uid":297981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:25:31.000Z","msg":"Block到手軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:28:30.000Z","msg":"我就唔block啦 可能一時on99跟風留言姐<br />\n不過<br />\n冇腦就收嗲啦你班撚屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2671a3d4091df0954921db27348535a4f055ef8e","tid":2117931,"uid":49524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:31:10.000Z","msg":"其實屌人好撚易架咋<br />\n一個唔高興連本土派都搵到位屌<br />\n<br />\n認清自己嘅敵人啦你班傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e009c5f385c781cea164a447264e8b5928b75964","tid":2117931,"uid":189157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:33:00.000Z","msg":"公道啲講<br />\n班醫護咁盡責咁有愛心<br />\n罷罷下工走返去返工<br />\n咁嘅時勢好應該共渡時姦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f3fd321b6b10b108e3b224542481c7bc8fcbd5","tid":2117931,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:38:07.000Z","msg":"嗰個post樓主講嘅野<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>除左面對有機會感染到武肺既危險 <br />\n仲要面對高層同ICN不斷搬龍門 <br />\n不斷降低醫護的保護裝備level <br />\n<br />\n無錯本身醫護人工唔低<br />\n但講呢啲既你地唔黎做？<br />\n日日面對1個護士對12-18個病人既工作量<br />\n屎尿血濃痰樣樣齊 <br />\n無間斷追更追到個人痴左線<br />\n冇武肺都會有愛滋 肺癆 呢啲傳染病要小心<br />\n<br />\n當啲黑警個個月拎住十萬去殺人打人<br />\n醫護拎三四萬去救人就好高好過份？<br />\n<br />\n呢家因為高層不斷搬龍門<br />\n好多醫護有家歸不得 要住酒店仲要被酒店既人嫌棄/拒絕入住<br />\n當然你地可以好順口講句「冇人逼你做」 <br />\n但我相信有部分醫護係真心為左幫人救人而做醫護 為錢個啲做唔得耐就拜拜<br />\n而點解罷工咁難都係咁解 但我地都照做左 但可惜都係變condom<br />\n無錯 可以辭職唔做 但個個醫護都咁諗 啲無辜有病既人點算？ <br />\n<br />\n標題淨打醫護其實唔夠 係所有醫院入面做野既同事 所有職系 不論職位高低 <br />\n只要係醫院做 今時今刻都為呢場人為災難做緊野</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7033838cedfc900bc562194c5b8e0863949c4681","tid":2117931,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b1d325385ea0fc381dce8d146bcee83b30699f","tid":2117931,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5107fcc6312b97eac4e858c92e14ae289e16c9cf","tid":2117931,"uid":49524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:58:16.000Z","msg":"係咁話人屈毛<br />\n<br />\n好 咪唔叫你五毛囉<br />\n不過又未撚見過班人係屌狗屌政府post咁積極發言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37020ec5a9b183fb2511d19d193a365c5128c3ce","tid":2117931,"uid":272202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:58:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗰堆人啲語氣用詞同2毛分化撚一鳩樣<br />\nblock到手軟"},{"pid":"3893f156532f43a54cf23f0893b2410b135539ab","tid":2117931,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37020ec5a9b183fb2511d19d193a365c5128c3ce","tid":2117931,"uid":272202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T07:58:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗰堆人啲語氣用詞同